          <h3>TWO ALARMS, LOTS OF SOUNDS</h3>
          <p>G-BUZZ is built with two alarms and a number of wake up sounds guaranteed to get you out of bed. You can wake up to a standard buzzer, or if you need something with a little more oomph you can wake up to rooster crowings, foghorns blowing, bells chiming or drums drumming. Prefer to wake up to your favorite radio station?<br>G-BUZZ can do that too!</p>
