          <h3>CONNECTS TO EVERYTHING
          <br>(THAT YOU ACTUALLY CARE ABOUT)</h3> 
          <p>G-BUZZ plays with any device that has a 3.5mm headphone jack. From your old school walkmans, record players and cassette decks (that you thought you would never use again), to current gadgets like your tablet or smartphone, it’s that easy to get your music playing with G-BUZZ.</p>
